item.title: CVE-2019-1010177|2024-08-05T03:07:18.412Z -- jsish -- jsi
item.description: Jsish 2.4.70 2.047 is affected by: Use After Free. The impact is: denial of service and possibly arbitrary code execution. The component is: function Jsi_RegExpNew (jsi/jsiRegexp.c:39). The attack vector is: executing crafted javascript code. The fixed version is: after commit 48a66c798d.
